title: Mame.Rom.Starter.Set.m172-99.6.Percent.Complete
description:
Tired of MAME "complete" romsets that aren't actually complete?   This set has been audited down to the checksums by ClrMamePro.   99.6% of the MAME 0.172 roms are here.   "Missing List" included. (138 of 31759 sets missing.  Gotta Catch 'Em All! :)

Split Sets.   Romsets "zipped" with 7-zip (it's the future!).  Disc 1, #-M.  Disc 2, N-Z.

(Note:  Wondering why these are stored as ISOs?   If the content was just a list of 7z files, the torrent file becomes too large for TPB to accept.   This is the best compromise.)

And BTW, a torrent with the missing roms would be very welcome, if someone is feeling industrious =]

share & enjoy
